Package eu.wauz.wauzcore.mobs.bestiary

This package contains classes, that are used for the bestiary system.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ObservationTracker
    A class to track the progress of the rank representing the detail level of a bestiary entry.
    WauzBestiaryEntry
    An entry of a bestiary species, generated from a bestiary config and a mythic mobs config file.
    WauzBestiarySpecies
    A species in a bestiary category, generated from a bestiary config file.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ObservationRank
    The rank representing the detail level of a bestiary entry.
    WauzBestiaryCategory
    The category of a section in the bestiary.
